'mesh/mesh_topology.h' (create_ method):
	We will need to handle creation of mixed-type sub-entities, e.g.,
	triangular vs. quadrilateral faces in 3D.  This is currently not
	handled correctly in the mesh topology.
	Update: Progress has been made on removing this constraint.

