	Mesh access of state model needs to be improved/clarified as per dual mesh
	coordinates and state.

'state/state.h'
	Add support for state collections.

'utils'
	Add Marc's static C++ utilities.

'mesh-based example of index spaces'
	Powerpoint slide of figures on simple mesh with vertices, edges, faces,
	cells and corners.
